Stateless & statefull widget
Every component is itself stateful widget like textView it extends statefull widget
stateless - no any changes on screen
statefull/onChange/setState - changes on screen (change welcome to "Welcome whtUserTypes")

Animation - Login btn collapse and change rectangle to circle  
Container - Create custom button
Backgroun color - 
Box decoration - if using this then must define bg color here not in container
GestureDetector - don't have ripple effect and other properties, no feedback
Inkwell - have ripple effect .. " onPress, onTap

